      • HarCacheRequest

        public HarCacheRequest(java.util.Date expires,
               java.util.Date lastAccess,
               java.lang.String tag,
               int hitCount,
               java.lang.String comment,
               boolean isBefore)
        Creates a new HarCacheRequest object
        Parameters:
        expires - expires [string, optional] - Expiration time of the cache entry.
        lastAccess - lastAccess [string] - The last time the cache entry was opened.
        tag - eTag [string] - Etag
        hitCount - hitCount [number] - The number of times the cache entry has been opened.
        comment - comment [string, optional] (new in 1.2) - A comment provided by the user or the application.
        isBefore - true if this is a beforeCache entry, false for an afterCache
